title: 35AWARDS 10th
content: I'm in the first [100 street photographers](https://35awards.com/winners2024/nomination/1021/photographers) in this year's 35AWARDS competition. Yet another little step in my photography journey.
By the way, I have a [visual diary on Instagram](https://instagram.com/sfi0zy/). No ads. No hype. No gear reviews. Just some street life and the reflections of my internal world.
